Charterhouse is working with a leading international law firm in Dubai.
Our client is looking to hire an exceptional Shipping and Transport Senior Associate to join their globally renowned shipping practice.
You will work directly with the Head of Department and act for some of the firmsâ leading clients dealing with the full range of superyacht and commercial shipping matters. You will also manage complex matters with minimum supervision from partners.
REQUIREMENTS
The ideal candidate should have gained a minimum of 8 years PQE with a leading international firm or shipping specialist law firm. You should also have excellent academics and a genuine desire to work for one of the top firms on some of the best work in the UAE. In return, you will be rewarded not only by the quality of the work and the team, but by a remuneration package which includes attractive bonuses.
Candidates should be either UK or US Qualified and have practiced in the London market.
ABOUT THE COMPANY
During the last ten years, Charterhouse has been operating across Dubai, Abu Dhabi and the GCC Markets. In many ways, we were the recruiter who established and set the standards within the regional recruitment industry benchmarking and innovating the service levels associated to Search and Selection.
Charterhouse understands the dynamics attached to talent acquisition, relationship management and the required service levels within the regional industry. Our heritage is now our main strength as we continue to work within our core markets to deliver key account management and strong contingency recruitment practices to our clients and candidates.
